overview: On March 31st get ready for the Josh Barnett's Bloodsport 8! Already announced is the first match - Minoru Suzuki will face off Chris Dickinson for one more time. Who will come out on top this time?  Plus:  Jon Moxley vs Biff Busick  Alex Coughlin vs Slade  Josh Barnett vs Jonah  Simon Grimm vs John Hennigan  Timothy Thatcher vs JR Kratos  Mike Bailey vs Yuya Uemura  Bad Dude Tito vs Royce Isaacs  Masha Slamovich vs Janai Kai  Ninja Mack vs Yoya  Zeda Zhang vs Marina Shafir
title: GCW Josh Barnett's Bloodsport 8
